# Only genuine, reproduced, minimized crashing inputs belong here; libFuzzer
# names them crash-<hash> and they are committed intentionally as regression
# artifacts. Do NOT move an un-triaged crash-<hash> here straight from the
# driver - a kill-artifact (the slow in-flight unit the driver dumps when it is
# killed mid-run) shares the same name but does not reproduce. Verify
# reproduction first; delete kill-artifacts instead of committing them.
# Transient driver output should not be committed.
*
!.gitignore
!crash-*
